Installation:
-------------

compile  :   make           [BUILD=path]
tests    :   make tests     [BUILD=path]
install  :   make install   [INSTALL=path]
uninstall:   make uninstall [BUILD=path] [INSTALL=path]

default build   path is .
default install path is /usr

Documentation:
--------------

INSTALL/share/doc/cos/

Program makefile:
-----------------

see CosBase/tests/Makefile

Project information:
--------------------
